title: Palestine Youth Unemployment Rate
description: Youth Unemployment Rate in Palestine increased to 37.70 percent in the third quarter of 2022 from 36.40 percent in the second quarter of 2022. Youth Unemployment Rate in Palestine averaged 42.23 percent from 2009 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 49.90 percent in the second quarter of 2018 and a record low of 32.90 percent in the first quarter of 2011. This page provides - Palestine Youth Unemployment Rate- actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Palestinian Central Bureau of Statistics
